description:
Do you get frustrated every time you try to create a photoshop design ?

Do you want to work in a magazine and you want some techniques in order to materialize your ideas ?

well, this course is for you! even if you are a beginner!

because in this course you're gonna learn every thing has to do with photo manipulation and also photo retouching !

And after completing this course and starting some discussions you're gonna be able to deal with your own projects easily.

so... What Are You Waiting For !
title: Photoshop killer designer - volume 1 (photo manipulation)
